Class ClassCreation

java.lang.Object
  xmlcomponents.autoparse.ClassCreation

public class ClassCreation
extends java.lang.Object

Class used for generating Java classes out of XML files. The generated class files are designed to be used in conjunction with the AutoParser. This is not quite ready for prime time...
